high_descs: turn right and head to the tub
pick up a bar soap from the tub
turn around and head to the sink
wet the soap in the sink
turn around and head to the bin
trash the soap in the bin
anns.task_desc: trash  a wet soap in the bin

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward, then hang a left and walk up to the tub.
Pick up the bar of soap off of the edge of the tub.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk up to the left sink.
Put the bar of soap in the left sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn off the water and remove the now clean bar of soap.
Walk over to the small silver bin in the corner of the room behind you.
Put the clean bar of soap in the silver bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap in a silver bin.

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk over to the bathtub.
Pick up the bar of soap that is lying on the edge of the tub.
Turn around and walk over to the bathroom counter that is now to your right.
Rinse off the bar of soap in the left sink basin before taking it back out.
Turn around completely and walk towards the trash bin in front of you.
Place the bar of soap in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Move a clean bar of soap to the trash bin.
